<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ja">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>お問い合わせありがとうございました | 将棋処やまと王将</title>
  <meta name="description" content="お問い合わせを受け付けました。ありがとうございます。">
</head>
<body>
  <div class="success-container">
    <div class="success-content">
      <div class="success-icon">
        <svg width="64" height="64" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
          <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10" stroke="#d32f2f" stroke-width="2"/>
          <path d="m9 12 2 2 4-4" stroke="#d32f2f" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/>
        </svg>
      </div>
      
      <h1>お問い合わせありがとうございました</h1>
      
      <div class="message-box">
        <p>お問い合わせを受け付けました。</p>
        <p>内容を確認の上、できるだけ早くお返事いたします。</p>
        <p>お急ぎの場合は、下記までお電話ください。</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="contact-info">
        <h2>お急ぎの場合</h2>
        <p class="phone">
          <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 1 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 1 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z" fill="#d32f2f"/>
          </svg>
          <a href="tel:090-8431-1107">090-8431-1107</a>
        </p>
        <p class="hours">営業時間: 12:00-19:00</p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="actions">
        <a href="/" class="back-button">ホームに戻る</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <script>
    // 5秒後に自動でホームページに戻る（オプション）
    setTimeout(() => {
      if (confirm('ホームページに戻りますか？')) {
        window.location.href = '/';
      }
    }, 10000);
  </script>
</body>
</html>

<style>
  * {
    margin: 0;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  body {
    font-family: 'Hiragino Sans', 'Noto Sans JP', sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: #333;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f5f7fa 0%, #c3cfe2 100%);
    min-height: 100vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: 20px;
  }

  .success-container {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .success-content {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 40px;
    text-align: center;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .success-icon {
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .success-icon svg {
    animation: checkmark 0.6s ease-in-out;
  }

  @keyframes checkmark {
    0% {
      transform: scale(0);
    }
    50% {
      transform: scale(1.2);
    }
    100% {
      transform: scale(1);
    }
  }

  h1 {
    color: #d32f2f;
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .message-box {
    background-color: #f8f9fa;
    border-left: 4px solid #d32f2f;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
    border-radius: 0 8px 8px 0;
  }

  .message-box p {
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .message-box p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .contact-info {
    background-color: #fff3e0;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 20px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
  }

  .contact-info h2 {
    color: #d32f2f;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 15px;
  }

  .phone {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 10px;
  }

  .phone a {
    color: #d32f2f;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: bold;
  }

  .phone a:hover {
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  .hours {
    color: #666;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .actions {
    margin-top: 30px;
  }

  .back-button {
    display: inline-block;
    background-color: #d32f2f;
    color: white;
    padding: 12px 30px;
    border-radius: 5px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: bold;
    transition: background-color 0.3s;
  }

  .back-button:hover {
    background-color: #b71c1c;
  }

  /* レスポンシブ対応 */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .success-content {
      padding: 30px 20px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }

    .phone a {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
  }
</style>